          <div class="p-6 p-text">
            <p>The total cost of flight training varies depending on how many hours you need, certificate sought, and airplane chosen. To gauge how much flight training might cost you, check out our <a class="text-sky-600 hover:underline" href="/approximate-pilot-training-costs">cost estimator page</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="relative border-b border-gray-200" x-data="{selected:null}">
        <button type="button" class="w-full px-8 py-6 text-left" @click="selected !== 4 ? selected = 4 : selected = null">
