            <p>SimpliFly offers training all the way up to certified flight instructor (CFI).  This includes private, instrument, commercial, multi-engine, and CFI training.  Many of our students have used the experience and training received here at SimpliFly and started successful airline carriers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
