            <p>Of course!  SimpliFly offers both flexible and accelerated programs to help you get your pilot certificate and ratings.  Check out our individual program pages for more details.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="relative border-b border-gray-200" x-data="{selected:null}">
