            <p>Of course! After you complete training at SimpliFly, we guarantee an interview to be a certified flight instructor (CFI). Being a CFI helps build experience and hours to help prepare you for further in your aviation career.  Check out our page about beginning your pilot career as a CFI for more details. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
